# Token Distributor

This project allows you to distribute tokens using Jito bundles on the Solana blockchain. It's designed to be easy to use, even for those new to command-line interfaces.

## Prerequisites

Before you begin, you'll need to install:

- [Git](https://git-scm.com/downloads)
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (which includes npm)

### For Windows Users

If you're using Windows, you'll need to set up the Windows Subsystem for Linux (WSL). Follow these steps:

1. Open PowerShell as Administrator and run:

wsl --install

2. Restart your computer when prompted.
3. After restart, open the "Ubuntu" app from the Start menu to set up your Linux username and password.

## Installation

1. Open your terminal (or Ubuntu terminal for Windows users).

2. Clone the repository:

2000IQ dev mode
