3. After restart, open the "Ubuntu" app from the Start menu to set up your Linux username and password.

## Installation

1. Open your terminal (or Ubuntu terminal for Windows users).

2. Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/token-distributor.git

3. Navigate to the project directory:

cd token-distributor

4. Install the required dependencies:

npm install

## Usage

To run the token distributor, use the following command:

node dist-tokens.js -k ./keypairs -r ./distri.txt -m TOKEN_MINT_ADDRESS -t TIP_ACCOUNT_ADDRESS

Replace `TOKEN_MINT_ADDRESS` with the address of the token you want to distribute, and `TIP_ACCOUNT_ADDRESS` with one of the following tip accounts:

- 96gYZGLnJYVFmbjzopPSU6QiEV5fGqZNyN9nmNhvrZU5
- HFqU5x63VTqvQss8hp11i4wVV8bD44PvwucfZ2bU7gRe
- Cw8CFyM9FkoMi7K7Crf6HNQqf4uEMzpKw6QNghXLvLkY
- ADaUMid9yfUytqMBgopwjb2DTLSokTSzL1zt6iGPaS49
- DfXygSm4jCyNCybVYYK6DwvWqjKee8pbDmJGcLWNDXjh
- ADuUkR4vqLUMWXxW9gh6D6L8pMSawimctcNZ5pGwDcEt
- DttWaMuVvTiduZRnguLF7jNxTgiMBZ1hyAumKUiL2KRL
- 3AVi9Tg9Uo68tJfuvoKvqKNWKkC5wPdSSdeBnizKZ6jT

### Options

- `-k, --key-folder <path>`: Path to the folder containing wallet key files (required)
- `-r, --recipient-file <path>`: Path to the file containing recipient addresses and amounts (required)
- `-m, --token-mint <address>`: Token mint address (required)
- `-t, --tip-account <address>`: Tip account address (required)
- `-a, --tip-amount <amount>`: Tip amount in lamports (default: 100000)

## File Formats

### Keypair Files

Place your Solana wallet keypair JSON files in the `keypairs` folder. An example keypair file is provided for reference.

### Recipient File

The recipient file (`distri.txt`) should contain one recipient per line in the format:

ADDRESS,AMOUNT

For example:
8SmfzHj35ZJXHQPMCWZrEHfdyWApykcSuRmuWNj193V2,100
EZ5LQMzATorMNsc4auJRHGRhy1eNffowUAKRqvFtkfu,420
DLvsEgCFfpmVeT1wW7eonc6n4om5jWbXF6shMHW3RZez,12

## Security Note

Never share your private keys or keypair files. The example keypair is for demonstration purposes only and should not be used on mainnet.

## Support

If you encounter any issues or have questions, please open an issue on the GitHub repository.

Happy token distributing!